    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7 NIGHTS KEEPER Demo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the eerie world of <i>7 NIGHTS KEEPER</i> in this exclusive demo. You’ll play as a caretaker tasked with surviving <strong>one night</strong> in Amaan’s mysterious mansion. In this demo, you’ll get a hands-on introduction to the core gameplay mechanics:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> a small, select portion of the mansion, including a few key rooms that set the stage for the full game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact</strong> with Amaan’s grandmother and uncover the first hints of something strange lurking in the house.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience</strong> the VHS-inspired visuals and haunting atmosphere that define <i>7 NIGHTS KEEPER</i>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/0c8c070d5cf0c847aa3b4530947cca3d.poster.avif?t=1731252900\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/0c8c070d5cf0c847aa3b4530947cca3d.webm?t=1731252900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/0c8c070d5cf0c847aa3b4530947cca3d.mp4?t=1731252900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is primarily a first-person narrative walking simulator with exploration, driving, and conversation mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/598952b67afa811dbaedf36800256336.poster.avif?t=1731252900\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/598952b67afa811dbaedf36800256336.webm?t=1731252900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242070/extras/598952b67afa811dbaedf36800256336.mp4?t=1731252900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Content Highlights:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore part of the mansion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic interactions with objects and NPCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive text messages that guide you through your tasks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A glimpse of the tension and horror that awaits in the full game.</p></li></ul>",
